




<section class="intro">

<h1 class="page_title round">Contact Us</h1>

</section>



<section> 

  	

    We are always looking for additional support. A contact point is currently being arranged (February 2012)
    and will be added as soon as possible. Do get in touch if you would either like to offer help or
    if you would like some advice on nature conservation in Mole Valley.

    
    

	<div class="wrapper">
		<div id="main" style="padding:50px 0 0 0;">

		<form id="contact-form" action="/" method="">
			<h3>Get in touch</h3>
			<h4>Fill in the form below, and we'll get back to you as soon as possible.</h4>
			<div>
				<label>
					<span>Name: (required)</span>
					<input placeholder="Please enter your name" type="text" tabindex="1" required autofocus>
				</label>
			</div>
			<div>
				<label>
					<span>Email: (required)</span>
					<input placeholder="Please enter your email address" type="email" tabindex="2" required>
				</label>
			</div>
			<div>
				<label>
					<span>Telephone: (optional)</span>
					<input placeholder="Please enter your number" type="tel" tabindex="3">
				</label>
			</div>
			<div>
				<label>
					<span>Message: (required)</span>
					<textarea placeholder="Include all the details you can" tabindex="5" required></textarea>
				</label>
			</div>
			<div>
				<button name="submit" type="submit" id="contact-submit">Send Email</button>
			</div>
		</form>
		<div class="contact-photo">
	<p>
	<%= image_tag("Adders-dancing.jpg", :alt => "Adders dancing", :class => "round") %>
	</p>
	</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
	

<section>
<p>
    <i>N.B. This page is currently being revised and an updated version will be provided shortly.</i>
</p>
</section>
